\n\n<div class=\""aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \"">\n    \n    <div class=\""container responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n    <div class=\""cmp-container mt-0 mb-0 pt-0 pb-60 px-0\"">\n        <div class=\""cmp-container__background gsi-container__background--image-repeat  \""></div>\n        \n\n\n<div class=\""aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \"">\n    \n    <div class=\""teaser cmp-teaser--gsi-pulse-card aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\""><div id=\""teaser-1322035beb\"" class=\""cmp-teaser\"">\n    \n    <div class=\""cmp-teaser__image\"">\n<div data-cmp-is=\""image\"" data-cmp-lazy data-cmp-lazythreshold=\""100\"" data-cmp-src=\""https://s7d1.scene7.com/is/image/goddardsysincqa/TOTY23_Pulse_Card_1?qlt=85&amp;wid=%7B.width%7D&amp;ts=1676937041983&amp;dpr=off\"" data-cmp-widths=\""300,400,500,600,700,800,900,1000,1100,1200\"" data-cmp-dmimage data-asset=\""/content/dam/gsi/campaigns/toty/2023/TOTY23_Pulse_Card_1.jpg\"" id=\""teaser-1322035beb-image\"" class=\""cmp-image\"" itemscope itemtype=\""http://schema.org/ImageObject\"">\n    \n        <noscript data-cmp-hook-image=\""noscript\"">\n            \n            <img src=\""https://s7d1.scene7.com/is/image/goddardsysincqa/TOTY23_Pulse_Card_1?qlt=85&ts=1676937041983&dpr=off\"" class=\""cmp-image__image\"" itemprop=\""contentUrl\"" data-cmp-hook-image=\""image\"" alt/>\n            \n        </noscript>\n    \n    \n    \n</div>\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n    <div class=\""cmp-teaser__content\"">\n        \n    \n\n        \n    \n\n        \n    <h2 class=\""cmp-teaser__title\"">\n        Teacher of the Year<br/>\n    </h2>\n\t\n\n        \n    <div class=\""cmp-teaser__description\""><p>Is there a special Goddard School teacher in your child’s life? Nominate them for Teacher of the Year!</p>\n</div>\n\n        \n    <div class=\""cmp-teaser__action-container\"">\n        \n    <a class=\""cmp-teaser__action-link\"" id=\""teaser-1322035beb-cta-60babab72a\"" href=\""https://www.goddardschoolteacheroftheyear.com\"" target=\""_blank\"">Submit a Nomination</a>\n\n    </div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\""container responsivegrid cmp-container--border-radius cmp-container--fixed-wide aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n    <div id=\""welcome-container\"" class=\""cmp-container mt-0 mb-0 pt-15 pt-lg-30 pb-15 pb-lg-30 px-10 px-lg-15\"">\n        <div class=\""cmp-container__background gsi-container__background--image-repeat  \"" style=\""background-color:#ffffff\""></div>\n        \n\n\n<div class=\""aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \"">\n    \n    <div class=\""title text-center text-uppercase aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\""><div id=\""title-5f8629b716\"" class=\""cmp-title mt-0 mb-15\"">\n    <h2 class=\""cmp-title__text \"" style=\""color:#d22730\"">\n        \n            Welcome to Our School\n            \n        \n    </h2>\n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class=\""text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n<div id=\""text-a007276555\"" class=\""cmp-text mt-0 mb-0 gsi-font-size-base\"" style=\""color: #002855\"">\n    \n        <p style=\""text-align: center;\"">The Goddard School of Randolph\u00A0is more than a warm and nurturing place. It's more than a great education for your child. It's peace of mind.</p>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class=\""text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\""faculty-spotlight responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n    \n\n\n\n    <div class=\""container-xxl\"">\n        <div class=\""row justify-content-center\"">\n            <div class=\""col-12\"">\n                <div class=\""cmp-teaser--faculty-spotlight\"">\n                    <div class=\""cmp-teaser\"">\n                        \n                        <div class=\""cmp-teaser__image\"">\n                            <img src=\""https://www-qa.goddardschool.com/content/dam/gsi/schools/nj/randolph/randolph/faculty/Molly-10108911698-1671134698777.jpeg/_jcr_content/renditions/original\"" class=\""cmp-image__image\"" alt=\""Meet  Molly\"" itemprop=\""contentUrl\"" data-cmp-hook-image=\""image\""/>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\""cmp-teaser__content\"">\n                            <h3 class=\""cmp-teaser__title\"">\n                                Meet  Molly\n                            </h3>\n                            <div class=\""cmp-teaser__sub-title\"">\n                                Director of Education\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\""cmp-teaser__description\"">\n                                Ms. Molly, our Director of Education, has a Bachelor's Degree in Elementary Education and English.  She has been with our school since 2010 and was instrumental in the development of our Kindergarten program which she also taught for 4 years.  In addition to being named “Teacher of the Year’ in 2012, her musical “Annie” and her month-long “China experience&quot; won her top honors.   Both her Math and Reading programs have been exceptional in preparing our children for first grade.  She has also been recognized by Randolph Elementary School Principals as an exceptional Educator.  Both of Ms. Molly's sons, Matthew and Andrew, started in our Infant program.  Matthew is a recent graduate and Andrew is currently in our Preschool program.\n                            </div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\""school-cards cards responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n    \n\n<div class=\""container-xxl\"">\n    <ul class=\""gsi-icon-card__list row justify-content-center\"">\n        \n    <li class=\""col-lg-3 mb-15\"">\n        <div class=\""card gsi-icon-card\"">\n            <img class=\""gsi-icon-card__icon\"" src=\""/content/dam/global/assets/icons/expanded/GS_VideoConference_Icon_Color_Expanded.png\"" alt=\""\""/>\n            <h3 class=\""h4\"">\n                Virtual Tour\n            </h3>\n            <div class=\""card-body\"">\n                <p>You and your family can now tour our School from the comfort of your home!</p>\n\n            </div>\n            <a href=\""/content/gsi/us/en/schools/nj/randolph/randolph/our-school/virtual-tour.html\"" class=\""gsi-link--cta\"">\n                <img class=\""gsi-link__icon\"" src=\""/etc.clientlibs/gsi/clientlibs/clientlib-site/resources/images/icon-circle-right-blue.svg\"" alt=\""\""/>\n                <span class=\""gsi-link__text\"">Take a Virtual Tour</span>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n    </li>\n\n    \n        \n    <li class=\""col-lg-3 mb-15\"">\n        <div class=\""card gsi-icon-card\"">\n            <img class=\""gsi-icon-card__icon\"" src=\""/content/dam/global/assets/icons/expanded/GS_Teacher_Icon_Color_Expanded_0.png\"" alt=\""\""/>\n            <h3 class=\""h4\"">\n                Faculty\n            </h3>\n            <div class=\""card-body\"">\n                <p>Our teachers blend the highest standards in early childhood education and development with nurturing care.</p>\n\n            </div>\n            <a href=\""/content/gsi/us/en/schools/nj/randolph/randolph/our-teachers.html\"" class=\""gsi-link--cta\"">\n                <img class=\""gsi-link__icon\"" src=\""/etc.clientlibs/gsi/clientlibs/clientlib-site/resources/images/icon-circle-right-blue.svg\"" alt=\""\""/>\n                <span class=\""gsi-link__text\"">Meet Our Teachers</span>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n    </li>\n\n    \n        \n    <li class=\""col-lg-3 mb-15\"">\n        <div class=\""card gsi-icon-card\"">\n            <img class=\""gsi-icon-card__icon\"" src=\""/content/dam/global/assets/icons/expanded/GS_Chess_Icon_Color_Expanded.png\"" alt=\""\""/>\n            <h3 class=\""h4\"">\n                Special Programs\n            </h3>\n            <div class=\""card-body\"">\n                <p>We enhance our play-based curriculum with a range of enrichment programs designed to fit your child’s interests.</p>\n\n            </div>\n            <a href=\""/content/gsi/us/en/schools/nj/randolph/randolph/our-school/special-programs.html\"" class=\""gsi-link--cta\"">\n                <img class=\""gsi-link__icon\"" src=\""/etc.clientlibs/gsi/clientlibs/clientlib-site/resources/images/icon-circle-right-blue.svg\"" alt=\""\""/>\n                <span class=\""gsi-link__text\"">See Our Programs</span>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n    </li>\n\n    \n        \n    <li class=\""col-lg-3 mb-15\"">\n        <div class=\""card gsi-icon-card\"">\n            <img class=\""gsi-icon-card__icon\"" src=\""/content/dam/global/assets/icons/expanded/GS_GoddardSchool_Icon_Color_Expanded.png\"" alt=\""\""/>\n            <h3 class=\""h4\"">\n                Our School\n            </h3>\n            <div class=\""card-body\"">\n                <p>Welcome! We’re committed to your child’s health, safety and education, which is why we provide children with safe and healthy learning environments at our School.</p>\n\n            </div>\n            <a href=\""/content/gsi/us/en/schools/nj/randolph/randolph/our-school.html\"" class=\""gsi-link--cta\"">\n                <img class=\""gsi-link__icon\"" src=\""/etc.clientlibs/gsi/clientlibs/clientlib-site/resources/images/icon-circle-right-blue.svg\"" alt=\""\""/>\n                <span class=\""gsi-link__text\"">Learn More</span>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n    </li>\n\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\""container responsivegrid aem-GridColumn--small--none aem-GridColumn--default--none aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--small--12 aem-GridColumn--offset--small--0 aem-GridColumn--default--12 aem-GridColumn--offs