esources/images/facebook-brands.svg\"" alt=\""\""/>\n                       <span class=\""gsi-link__text\"">Facebook</span>\n                  </a>\n             </li>\n             <li class=\""nav-item\"" role=\""presentation\"" data-tab-content-id=\""instagram\"">\n                  <a href=\""#instagram\"" id=\""instagramTab\"" class=\""nav-link instagram\"" data-toggle=\""tab\"" role=\""tab\"" aria-controls=\""instagram\"" aria-selected=\""true\"">\n                       <img class=\""gsi-school-social__feed-icon mr-5\"" src=\""/etc.clientlibs/gsi/clientlibs/clientlib-site/resources/images/instagram-brands.svg\"" alt=\""\""/>\n                       <span class=\""gsi-link__text\"">Instagram</span>\n                  </a>\n             </li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\""gsi-school-social__tab-content tab-content\"">\n        </div>\n   </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\""container responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n    <div class=\""cmp-container mt-0 mb-0 pt-0 pb-0 px-0\"">\n        <div class=\""cmp-container__background gsi-container__background--image-repeat  \""></div>\n        \n\n\n<div class=\""aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \"">\n    \n    <div class=\""school-testimonials-carousel responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n    \n\n\n<div class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel\"" style=\""background-image: url(/content/dam/gsi/school-testimonials-bg.png);\"">\n    <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel__header\"">\n        <img src=\""/content/dam/global/assets/icons/expanded/GS_Family_Icon_Color_Expanded.png\"" alt=\""Heading icon\"" class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel__icon\""/>\n        <h2 class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel__heading\"">\n            <span class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel__heading-line1\"">GODDARD LOVE FROM</span>\n            <span class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel__heading-line2\"">FAMILIES LIKE YOURS</span>\n        </h2>\n        \n        <a href=\""/content/gsi/us/en/schools/nj/randolph/randolph/reviews-recognition\"" class=\""gsi-link--cta gsi-link--light\"">\n            <img class=\""gsi-link__icon\"" src=\""/etc.clientlibs/gsi/clientlibs/clientlib-site/resources/images/icon-circle-right-light-blue.svg\"" alt=\""\""/>\n            <span class=\""gsi-link__text\"">Read More</span>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel__carousel\"" id=\""gsiSchoolTestimonialsCarousel\"">\n        <blockquote class=\""gsi-school-testimonial\"">\n            <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__quote\"">The Goddard school in Randolph is like an extended family. From John and Anne and Jonathan running everything, to Michelle and Collette in the office, to the teachers in all the classrooms, and even the other parents, everyone makes you feel welcomed and appreciated. I can honestly say that we have not had a single negative experience with anyone there. Our daughter has flourished under the care and guidance of her wonderful teachers and has many friends. Goddard is wonderful.</div>\n            <footer>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__name h3\"">Keira&#39;s Father</div>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__title\"">Preschool Classroom</div>\n            </footer>\n        </blockquote>\n    \n        <blockquote class=\""gsi-school-testimonial\"">\n            <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__quote\"">The owners, directors and teachers may very well be the best in the industry as far as I'm concerned.  I hardly every think about the baby while I'm at work and it's not because I don't care about him it's because I truly 200% trust he's being loved, taught, and well taken care of.  I'd recommend this school to anyone and everyone!</div>\n            <footer>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__name h3\"">Antonio&#39;s Mother</div>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__title\"">Infant Classroom</div>\n            </footer>\n        </blockquote>\n    \n        <blockquote class=\""gsi-school-testimonial\"">\n            <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__quote\"">The children appear consistently engaged and everyone seems as if they're having fun, including the teachers. The teachers and owners greet us (the parents and children) with smiles when we're coming and going, there always seems to be some new, exciting activity in the works, and I get the impression that everyone who works there sincerely cares about the children. It's just a very positive and welcoming environment.</div>\n            <footer>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__name h3\"">David&#39;s Father</div>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__title\"">Preschool Classroom</div>\n            </footer>\n        </blockquote>\n    \n        <blockquote class=\""gsi-school-testimonial\"">\n            <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__quote\"">Our daughter has been with Goddard since she was 4.5 months old - now she has just turned 5 years old.  The owners and staff have always treated us like family.  There is always a welcoming face to greet you when you come in the door and the teachers are some of the best!  I couldn't have asked for a better experience for our daughter to start school.</div>\n            <footer>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__name h3\"">Caitlin&#39;s Mother</div>\n                <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonial__title\"">Pre-K Classroom</div>\n            </footer>\n        </blockquote>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\""gsi-school-testimonials-carousel__controls\""></div>\n</div></div>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\""image-cards responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\"">\n    \n\n<div class=\""gsi-image-cards\"">\n    \n        \n    <div class=\""gsi-image-card gsi